parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the O/D light flashes
the vehicle jerks or bucks
the transmission shifts erratically
the vehicle loses power
the transmission fails to engage into gear
the transmission overheats
and the vehicle surges forward.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended airbag deployment can cause injuries, distractions, and accidents, especially if it occurs while driving. It can also lead to unnecessary repair costs and vehicle downtime.
symptoms: Airbags deploy without a crash or impact
sudden explosion of airbags
smoke and flying shrapnel
injuries from airbag deployment
and damage to the vehicle's interior.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can increase the risk of injury or fatality to the occupants.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
injuries or fatalities due to lack of airbag deployment
and damage to the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Airbag sensor malfunction can cause unintended airbag deployment or failure of airbags to deploy in a crash, leading to injuries, accidents, and unnecessary repair costs.
symptoms: Airbag sensor flashing
airbag light on
and airbag deployment without a crash or impact.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or hesitate while driving, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle stalls or shuts off while driving
the overdrive light blinks on and off
the vehicle is difficult to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine overheating can cause damage to the engine and other components, leading to costly repairs and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The temperature gauge rises to the red zone
the vehicle overheats
coolant leaks
the engine shuts off while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Clutch failure can cause the vehicle to stall or hesitate while driving, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the vehicle is difficult to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failure can cause the vehicle to stall or shut off while driving, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The check engine light comes on
the overdrive light blinks on and off
the vehicle shuts off while driving
the battery explodes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine component failure can cause damage to the engine and other components, leading to costly repairs and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The engine mounts corrode and break
the hydraulic valve lifter fails
the valve cover gasket fails
the head gasket leaks oil into spark plugs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Power train failure can cause the vehicle to stall or hesitate while driving, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
the transmission slips or hesitates
the overdrive light blinks on and off.
